 identities, artificial intelligence, or the Internet of Things. His research involves information systems engineering and IT strategy and (risk) management, as well as regulatory compliance. In his projects and partnerships, he collaborates with partners in financial services, energy, mobility, manufacturing, and consulting, as well as with public bodies and governments.}
